    // >2.5s = Verisium/breach/utility took over -> don't false-ban), or when we get CLOSER. No-closer for
    // PREBOSS_REQ_STUCK_MS while actively fog-routing = this beacon is unreachable -> BAN it 2min + concede this frame so
